\">RUC Soundings (skew-t) weather info</a>\r\n\r\n<h2>Race Results</h2>\r\n\r\nBay to Breakers 12k 5/17/2009- 1:19:52 Pace: 10:43\r\nSeattle Rock and Roll Half Marathon 6/27/2009- 1:58:06 Pace: 9:03\r\nMicrosoft Giving Campaign 5k Run 10/9/2009- 24:34.9 Pace: 7:55\r\nLas Vegas Rock and Roll Half Marathon 12/6/2009- 1:55:40 Pace: 8:50\r\nSurf City USA Half Marathon (Huntington Beach) 2/7/2010- 2:03:10 Pace: 9:24\r\nPortland Run for the Cheetah 3/28/2010- 0:40:11 Pace: 8:05    <a href=\"http://www.racecenter.com/results/2010/res_c810.htm\">-3rd Place in Sex/Age Group-</a>\r\nBig Sur 9-Mile 4/25/2010- 1:16:19 Pace 8:28\r\nBay to Breakers 12k 5/16/2010- 1:04:41 Pace 8:37\r\nSeattle Rock and Roll Half Marathon 6/26/2010- DNF- Sprained ankle\r\nBellingham Half Marathon 9/26/2010- 02:00:53 Pace 9:16 \r\nMicrosoft Giving Campaign 5k Run 10/15/2010- 24:55.2 Pace: 8:02\r\nSt. Patty\'s Day Dash 3.8 miles 3/13/2011- 32:31 Pace: 8:34\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n','Miscellaneous',0,'','inherit','open','open','','499-revision-12','','','2011-03-13 14:31:56','2011-03-13 21:31:56','',499,'http://www.alexhopmann.com/2011/03/13/499-revision-12/',0,'revision','',0),(641,2,'2010-12-30 00:01:39','2010-12-30 07:01:39','<h1>Seattle</h1>\r\n\r\n<b>Places I Love</b>\r\n<em>These are the top places I\'d recommend to someone from out-of-town</em>\r\nNishino\r\nPoppy\r\nLark\r\nDahlia Lounge\r\nLa Carta De Oaxaca‎\r\nDelancey\r\n\r\n<b>Regular Spots</b>\r\n<em>These are the places we go all the time</em>\r\nPoppy\r\nSt. Clouds\r\nMio Posto\r\nBoom\r\n<a href=\"http://bistroturkuaz.com\">Bistro Turkuaz</a>‎ (34th Ave)\r\n<a href=\"http://cantinettaseattle.com/\">Cantinetta in Wallingford</a>\r\n\r\n<b>Places to Try (or try again)</b>\r\nVoila Bistro Madison St.\r\nCrush\r\nFu Man’s- Dumplings.\r\nArtisanal Table handmade pappardelle noodles\r\nSpinasse The eggy tajarin noodles with butter and sage \r\nMondello  Sexy spaghetti carbonara \r\nManna Deli & Teriyaki, cater-corner from the 5 Seasons Grill - Teriyaki wraps\r\nSALAAMA, a Somali roadhouse near SEATAC Teriyaki\r\n5 Seasons Grill, Vietnamese \r\nTokyo Garden’s Nepal Teriyaki + Nepalese dumplings, known as momo\r\nPlaka Estiatorio (Ballard)\r\nSquare Lotus (Factoria)\r\nArt of the Table (tiny, Wallingford)\r\nBisato (Carsberg)\r\nCicchetti (Eastlake)\r\nThe Corson Building (for dinner, brunch was great)\r\nEmmer and Rye (Queen Anne)\r\nHomegrown (sandwiches)\r\nJune (Madrona)\r\nMarination (Mobile, <a href=\"http://marinationmobile.com\">http://marinationmobile.com</a> )\r\nMistral Kitchen Tasting Menu\r\nQuinn\'s\r\nPortage (Queen Anne)\r\nSambar (Ballard)\r\nSpur Gastropub (Belltown)\r\nStaple and Fancy Mercantile (Ballard)\r\nVerve Bistro and Celllar (Columbia City)\r\nThe Walrus and the Carpenter (Ballard)\r\nWild Ginger (Bellevue serves Dim Sum now on weekends?)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1>New York</h1>\r\n\r\n<b>Places I Love</b>\r\nBalthazar\r\nDanube\r\nKatz\'s Deli\r\nTotonno\'s Pizzeria - Brooklyn (NOT the Manhattan one)\r\nwd~50\r\n\r\n<b>Places to Try (or try again)</b>\r\n<a href=\"http://events.nytimes.com/2009/05/20/dining/reviews/20rest.html?hpw\">Minetta Tavern</a> - Steak Place in NY\r\n\r\n<h1>Portland</h1>\r\n<b>Places I Love</b>\r\n<a href=\"http://simpaticacatering.com/\">Simpatica</a>- Amazing brunch, apparently has dinner now on Friday and Saturday, I need to check that out.\r\n\r\n<b>Places to Try (or try again)</b>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.laurelhurstmarket.com/\">Laurelhurst Market</a>- From the Simpatica folks, butcher by day, steakhouse by night. Also need to check this out.\r\n\r\n\r\n<h1>Las Vegas</h1>\r\n<b>Places I Love</b>\r\nL\'Atelier de Joël Robuchon\r\n\r\n<b>Places to Try (or try again)</b>\r\nBartolotta Ristorante di Mare - Wynn\r\n\r\n<h1>Wineries to Check Out</h1>\r\nVilla Creek Cellars (Paso Robles)\r\nRound Pound Estate (Rutherford, Napa)\r\n','Restaurants',0,'','inherit','open','open','','487-revision-20','','','2010-12-30 00:01:39','2010-12-30 07:01:39','',487,'http: