eam that designed and and implemented the next generation service that is a component of Office 365. Created the service fabric for automatic deployment and adopted traditional on-premises software to run as a service on thousands of servers.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>2012-Now Microsoft Corporation  Redmond, WA\r\nDevelopment Lead, Xbox Platform\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Member of the team delivering the Xbox One software platform for user interface applications.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 10px 0px 0px\"><strong>Education</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding:10px 0px 0px 0px\">1989-1993 Cornell University, Ithaca, NY\r\nB.A. Physics, concentration in Computer Science.\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr><td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"padding:8px 0px 0px 0px\">1985-1989 Classical High School, Providence, RI</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 10px 0px 0px\"><strong>Other</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"padding:-36px 0px 0px 0px\">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -20px\">Granted 16 patents, others pending.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -20px\">Contributed to design of HTTP 1.1, HTML 4.0, XML 1.0, WebDAV, CDF/RSS.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -20px\">Co-inventor of AJAX, Co-Author of Internet Standards MHTML, PICS</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3><a href=\"http://web.uvic.ca/akeller/Reviews/WebForOne.html\">MacWeek review of Web For One</a></h3>\r\nMy favorite quote-\r\n<p class=\"header-pagesub\">\"So easy an adult could do it\"</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 class=\"DateHeader\">Interests</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Music</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.lancairtalk.com/\">Flying Airplanes</a></li>\r\n	<li>Wine</li>\r\n	<li>Skiing</li>\r\n	<li>Soccer (Playing & <a href=\"http://www.soundersfc.com/\">Sounders FC</a></li>\r\n	<li>Travel</li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"http://www.tastingmenu.com/\">Food</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.shirle