://www.janerichlovsky.com/\">Jane Richlovsky</a>\r\n\r\nRick Bartow\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://michelemikesell.com/\">Michele Mikesell</a>\r\n\r\nJudith Kindler\r\n\r\nTyson Grumm\r\n\r\nBrett Rogers\r\n\r\nZ.Z. Wei\r\n\r\nPatrick Lociccero\r\n\r\nAdde Russell\r\n\r\nCalvin Ma','Art',0,'','inherit','open','open','','593-revision-4','','','2013-11-10 10:41:09','2013-11-10 17:41:09','',593,'http://www.alexhopmann.com/2013/11/10/593-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(672,2,'2014-03-22 17:11:40','2014-03-23 00:11:40','<div>This page is a place to list hikes and backpacking/camping that I\'ve done and others that I would like to do at some point in the future.</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Hikes I\'ve done</h2>\r\n<h3>USA- Washington State</h3>\r\n\r\n<div>Skookum Flats Trail #1194- NW of Mt. Ranier</div>\r\n<div>Little Si</div>\r\n<div>Tiger Mountain</div>\r\n<div>Bike the iron horse trail</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>USA- Montana</h3>\r\n<div>Glacier National Park</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>USA- California</h3>\r\n<div>Yosemite- Tuolamie</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Hikes I\'d love to do in the future</h2>\r\n<h3>USA- Washinton State</h3>\r\n\r\n<div>The Enchantments (Cascades)</div>\r\n<div>Wonderland Trail (Mt Ranier)</div>\r\n<div>Anything in the Olympics</div>\r\n<h3>USA- Utah</h3>\r\n<div>Zion National Park</div>\r\n<h3>USA- California</h3>\r\n<div>Yosemite- El Capitan</div>\r\n','Hiking',0,'','inherit','open','open','','116-revision-v1','','','2014-03-22 17:11:40','2014-03-23 00:11:40','',116,'http://www.alexhopmann.com/2014/03/22/116-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(673,2,'2014-03-22 17:15:08','2014-03-23 00:15:08','<div>This page is a place to list hikes and backpacking/camping that I\'ve done and others that I would like to do at some point in the future.</div>\r\n\r\n<h2>Hikes I\'ve done</h2>\r\n<h3>USA- Washington State</h3>\r\n\r\n<div>Skookum Flats Trail #1194- NW of Mt. Ranier</div>\r\n<div>Little Si</div>\r\n<div>Tiger Mountain</div>\r\n<div>Bike the iron horse trail</div>\r\n\r\n<h3>USA- Montana</h3>\r\